text:
🏋️Fitness Corner, Opp Blk 405 is located by the side of the walkway in front of Blk 405 Fajar Rd.
🧗Consisting of basic core muscle strengthening exercise equipments, the conveniently located Fitness Corner is accessible to all 24/7 and free-of-charge.
👣No need to spend time travelling to a gym. Whatever little time you have is all put into actual training itself.
This is just great!😘
